steering behaviours adopted from source:
https://unisalesianogames.files.wordpress.com/2011/08/programming-game-ai-by-example-mat-buckland2.pdf?hc_location=ufi

To view examples uncomment demo in game.js file and run index.html
If running locally, will need to enable in browser
e.g.
To enable in Chrome locally:
-close all current windows
-create a new shortcut (rename local to differentiate)
-right click shortcut and select properties
-append "--allow-file-access-from-files" to target
-open this shortcut and run here